enhanced_by.reason: The account method provides the current state of the margin account, which is necessary to validate the parameters and ensure the account has sufficient balance before placing a new order.
The allAssets method provides information about all available assets, which can be used to validate the asset parameters before placing a new order.
The getOrder method retrieves details of a specific order, which can be used to verify the correctness of the new order placement by comparing the returned order details with the expected values.
The getOpenOrders method retrieves all open orders, which can be used to verify that the new order has been successfully placed and is included in the list of open orders.
